(4, 0, 1, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(5, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1507093587, 1507093587, 1507093418, 0, '那些年，我们一起迷茫过的职业定位 ', '', '', '\n&lt;p style=''padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: justify; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;1、  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    对于即将面临就业的大学生，我发现了一个共同的问题。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    很多人不知道怎么去定位好自己未来的职业。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    于是我决定继续不要脸地写一些文字在这里,帮助大家去定位好自己，我的观点有两个：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    一。 职业定位的思路应该是 地域---行业----企业----职位。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    二。 职业定位需要不断调整&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    仅供参考，个人整合，没有想过误人子弟，建议辩证思考。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;2、观点一：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    关于职业定位的方法,其实网上很多文章都有说,我认为最好的思路就是：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    地域-----行业-----企业-----职业&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    (PS:这是我之前从一位前辈的空间里转载的文章里的观点,很受用，在此借用)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    按照这个思路，我想举个例子来表达一个精确的职业定位，比方说，小明决定了毕业之后要留在广州，进入ＦＭＣＧ行业，进入宝洁（中国）总部ｍａｒｋｅｔｉｎｇ部门，做管理培训生。这样的定位就是很具体的，并且从这点看，小明是很有勇气很有理想的。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    下面，我会针对以上四个要素,提出我的一些看法：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    一，确定自己的工作地域要和家里人商量。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    考虑工作城市的时候，除了考虑工作城市的经济水平和政策优势之外，希望大家也要考虑一下家里人的感受，工作不是生活的全部,男儿女儿志在四方是好事，但是要让家里人放心，不能只顾自己的意愿。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;     二,确定自己想进的行业要充分考虑发展前景。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    俗语说,男人最怕入错行,其实女生同样伤不起。考虑行业的发展前景，行业发展前景的主要影响因素就是政策和市场。我建议大家多去了解一下国家政策和近年的行业报告。因为在中国，政策决定经济走向,行业报告代表了市场状况。通过这样的判断，你应该会找到自己比较看好的行业，结合自己的专业和兴趣，你需要确定好几个行业，然后&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    你要开始关注这些行业。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    关注一个行业，可通过媒体信息去了解相关信息。比方说你关注房地产业，你可以了解到现在房地产行业在调整，有可能重新洗牌，房产税也在准备扩大试点范围，最近的市场反应还不错，广州等一线城市的交易量有上升。你也应该要阅读一些行内名人的博客，例如房地产，我们可以看看去叶檀的新浪博客。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    关注一个行业，也可了解一下从业人员的生存状态。我们可以去关心一下师兄师姐的生活状态，我们可以通过论坛里面的帖子去看看别人的吐槽。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    关注一段时间，相信你渐渐会有一些自己的理解，这些理解能帮助你判断一个行业是不是适合你自己。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    三，选择你想去的企业要考虑企业水平和自己条件的匹配程度&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    我相信很多人都向往一份世界５００强高薪体面的工作，我希望大家不要迷恋５００强，想想看，凤姐也是５００强（家乐福）的员工，囧，所以。。。我们可以看得更广一点。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;     很多不是５００强的企业，在行业内的实力也是不错的，所以可以多去了解一下这些企业，不要只盯着那些牛企。虽然，我们都希望毕业能够去一家顶级名企工作，但是竞争是很激烈的，我们也需要考虑自己的条件是否能够匹配这份工作。林夕写给王菲的＜给自己的情书＞里有一句歌词，＂仰望到太高，贬低的只有自己＂，个中含义异曲同工。非常建议大家去看看自己心仪企业对应届生的要求，去百度搜索＂ＸＸ企业校园招聘＂就会看到，从现在开始评估一下自己现在能不能符合这些要求，在未来的时间里，缺什么补什么。比方说，银行需要通过４级考试，那么你想进银行，你要考过４级。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;     在和一些师弟师妹的交流中，我一般都会去了解他们大学期间的经历，结合他们想去的企业，让他们对自己现在的能力做一个评估，方便他们在接下来的时间里不断提高自己。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;     企业对外宣讲时总是说他们只选择最适合的人才，不论专业学校，但是这个社会还是有门槛的，所以要做好失败的准备。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;     四，选择你的职业要具体企业内的某一个职位。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;     和师弟师妹的沟通中，我很欣慰地看到了很多人都有了自己的想法，尽管有些想法不够具体，但是有想法永远比没想法好嘛，＾＾。有人告诉我他想进入宝洁，但是当我问及他想什么部门的时候，他反问我宝洁有什么部门。为了让大家可以更清晰地去定位自己， 我希望大家把目标具体到某一个职位。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    校园招聘中，企业提供给应届生的职位有很多类型，销售，财务，人力资源，而在这些类别里面也有不同的职位，从现在开始去了解这些职位，把自己的目标明确好。   &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    对于不同类型的工作要求的能力也会有不同，我建议大家可以做一些职业测评和性格测试，在网上搜索有很多，比较权威的有ＭＢＩＴ的职业测评，九型人格性格测试，大家可以去做一做，了解一下自己。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    我也建议大家通过实习去了解一下不同的职位，尽管有不少实习都是打杂，但是我们还是可以通过观察和沟通去了解企业内部不同的分工各自的职责是什么。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;     总之，我建议把自己的目标定位在企业内的某一个职位，这样做可以方便我们更有意识地提高自己的能力，去积累相关的知识。同时要提醒大家，不要只盯着某家企业的某个职位，非此不去，这样很危险的，一开始还是要广撒网，有ｏｆｆｅｒ保底了可以挑着去面试。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;3、观点二：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    我相信通过观点一的思路，大家可以掌握到一些职业定位的方法，这样在求职的时候，我们会有自己明确的目标，但是我们都不能保证自己能够达到预期目标。所以接下来我想分享另一个观点，职业定位需要不断调整。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    首先，我们需要不断调整自己的心态。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    对于心仪的企业，或许我们会在网申的阶段就挂掉，或许我们会进入笔试面试再挂，或许我们会拿到ｏｆｆｅｒ，这一整个历程，其实不单单是在考验我们的能力，也考验我们的心态。尤其是失败的时候，更考验我们的逆商。我建议大家在求职失败的时候，少一点去悲观吐槽，花多一点时间去看其他企业的招聘信息。因为消极的行为只会让我们更消极，要走出失败，要让自己看到新的希望。或许我们一直都被教育如何去获得成功，但是很少有人教我们怎么在跌倒的时候，怎么有尊严地爬起来，然而能够在失败面前及时爬起来本身就是一种巨大的成功。我相信有积极的心态，很多事情绝对没有你想得那么坏。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    此处不留爷，只有留爷处嘛，对不对？要积极一点。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    其次，我们需要不断调整自己的求职目标。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    求职的过程，除了大牛和空降兵，我相信大部分人的经历都不是一帆风顺的，所以我们要不断调整自己的求职目标。我建议大家把心仪的企业排一个序，分成不同级别的目标，时刻调整自己的求职目标。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    要事先做好求职目标的管理，因为在求职的过程中，一切都是未知数。这样的做法就像保险，让未知的挫折变得好接受些。并且这样的做法可以帮助我们尽快把注意力从失败中离开，把注意力放在下一级别的目标。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    另外，我希望大家把目标定高一点。求其上，得其中，求其中，得其下。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    有句话说得好，人不逼一下自己，你永远不知道自己有多优秀。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    所以，目标远大绝对不是不自量力，而是力争上游。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;    最后，我希望大家找工作的时候不要有攀比的心态，找工作不是要找最好的，而是要找最适合自己的。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;４、     &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;关于职业定位的问题，我的主要观点到此为止。回想当初自己没有很充分地做好自己的职业定位，误打误撞地尝试了不同的企业和职位，一路折腾效率不高。庆幸的是，我因为机缘巧合进入了自己想进的企业，一路感恩，尤其知遇之恩。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=''text-align: justify; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;''&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(70, 68, 69); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt; 在此希望各位可以更有效率地定位好自己，保持一份乐观的心态不断调整自己，迎接离你们不远的求职挑战，收获最理想的ｏｆｆｅｒ。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n', NULL, '{"thumbnail":""}');
